        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.073,
                0.136,
                0.162,
                0.151
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "一、填空题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.073,
                0.158,
                0.217,
                0.186
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 \\(\\frac{1}{3}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.194,
                0.592,
                0.226
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\left(\\frac{1}{x^2} -\\frac{1}{x\\tan x}\\right) = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\tan x - x}{x^2\\tan x} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\tan x - x}{x^3}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.32,
                0.232,
                0.506,
                0.261
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\sec^ {2} x - 1}{3 x ^ {2}} = \\frac {1}{3}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.073,
                0.268,
                0.24,
                0.283
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 \\(\\sin x^2\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.289,
                0.674,
                0.318
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\(\\int_0^x\\sin (x - t)^2\\mathrm{d}t\\xlongequal{x - t = u}\\int_x^0\\sin u^2 (-\\mathrm{d}u) = \\int_0^x\\sin u^2\\mathrm{d}u\\) 得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.331,
                0.324,
                0.717,
                0.353
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\frac {\\mathrm {d}}{\\mathrm {d} x} \\int_ {0} ^ {x} \\sin (x - t) ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} t = \\frac {\\mathrm {d}}{\\mathrm {d} x} \\int_ {0} ^ {x} \\sin u ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} u = \\sin x ^ {2}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.073,
                0.362,
                0.564,
                0.389
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【答案】 \\(C_1\\mathrm{e}^{-2x} + C_2\\mathrm{e}^{2x} + \\frac{1}{4} x\\mathrm{e}^{2x}(C_1,C_2\\) 为任意常数）."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.396,
                0.595,
                0.412
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 特征方程为 \\(\\lambda^2 - 4 = 0\\)，特征根为 \\(\\lambda_1 = -2, \\lambda_2 = 2\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.103,
                0.417,
                0.488,
                0.434
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(y^{\\prime \\prime} - 4y = 0\\) 的通解为 \\(y = C_{1}\\mathrm{e}^{-2x} + C_{2}\\mathrm{e}^{2x}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.103,
                0.44,
                0.597,
                0.468
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "令 \\(y^{\\prime \\prime} - 4y = \\mathrm{e}^{2x}\\) 的特解为 \\(y_0(x) = ax\\mathrm{e}^{2x}\\) ，代入得 \\(a = \\frac{1}{4}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.476,
                0.749,
                0.503
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(y^{\\prime \\prime} - 4y = \\mathrm{e}^{2x}\\) 的通解为 \\(y = C_{1}\\mathrm{e}^{-2x} + C_{2}\\mathrm{e}^{2x} + \\frac{1}{4} x\\mathrm{e}^{2x}(C_{1},C_{2}\\) 为任意常数)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.073,
                0.511,
                0.464,
                0.527
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 \\(\\lambda_{1} = \\lambda_{2} = \\dots = \\lambda_{n - 1} = 0, \\lambda_{n} = n\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.531,
                0.801,
                0.611
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】方法一 由 \\(|\\lambda E - A| = \\left| \\begin{array}{cccc}\\lambda -1 & -1 & \\dots & -1\\\\ -1 & \\lambda -1 & \\dots & -1\\\\ \\vdots & \\vdots & & \\vdots \\\\ -1 & -1 & \\dots & \\lambda -1 \\end{array} \\right| = \\lambda^{n - 1}(\\lambda -n) = 0\\) 得"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.616,
                0.51,
                0.632
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\mathbf{A}\\) 的特征值为 \\(\\lambda_{1} = \\lambda_{2} = \\dots = \\lambda_{n - 1} = 0, \\lambda_{n} = n\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.637,
                0.801,
                0.653
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "方法二 因为 \\( \\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}} = \\mathbf{A} \\)，所以 \\( \\mathbf{A} \\) 可对角化，从而 \\( \\mathbf{A} \\) 的非零特征值的个数与 \\( r(\\mathbf{A}) \\) 相同，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.103,
                0.659,
                0.438,
                0.674
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(r(\\mathbf{A}) = 1\\) 得 \\(A\\) 只有一个非零特征值，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.679,
                0.868,
                0.695
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "又因为 \\(\\operatorname{tr} A = n = \\lambda_1 + \\lambda_2 + \\dots + \\lambda_n\\)，所以 \\(A\\) 的特征值为 \\(\\lambda_1 = \\lambda_2 = \\dots = \\lambda_{n-1} = 0, \\lambda_n = n\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.073,
                0.702,
                0.217,
                0.729
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(5)【答案】 \\(\\frac{1}{4}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.736,
                0.292,
                0.752
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 令 \\(P(A) = p\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.756,
                0.829,
                0.772
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "而 \\(P(A \\cup B \\cup C) = P(A) + P(B) + P(C) - P(AB) - P(AC) - P(BC) + P(ABC)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.268,
                0.777,
                0.377,
                0.793
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= 3 p - 3 p ^ {2},\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.103,
                0.799,
                0.473,
                0.827
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(3p - 3p^2 = \\frac{9}{16}\\) ，解得 \\(p = \\frac{1}{4}\\) 或 \\(p = \\frac{3}{4}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.104,
                0.835,
                0.364,
                0.863
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(P(A) < \\frac{1}{2}\\) 得 \\(P(A) = \\frac{1}{4}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.073,
                0.87,
                0.162,
                0.885
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "二、选择题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.073,
                0.891,
                0.222,
                0.905
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（1）【答案】 （A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.911,
                0.48,
                0.938
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 若 \\(f(x)\\) 是奇函数，\\(F(x) = \\int_{a}^{x} f(t) \\, \\mathrm{d}t\\)"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.077,
                0.07,
                0.607,
                0.098
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(F(-x) = \\int_{a}^{-x}f(t)\\mathrm{d}t\\frac{t = -u}{-a}\\int_{-a}^{x}f(-u)(-\\mathrm{d}u) = \\int_{-a}^{x}f(u)\\mathrm{d}u\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.173,
                0.105,
                0.566,
                0.133
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\int_ {- a} ^ {a} f (u) \\mathrm {d} u + \\int_ {a} ^ {x} f (u) \\mathrm {d} u = \\int_ {a} ^ {x} f (u) \\mathrm {d} u = F (x),\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.077,
                0.14,
                0.315,
                0.154
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "即 \\(F(x)\\) 为偶函数，应选(A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.046,
                0.161,
                0.192,
                0.175
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 (D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.077,
                0.182,
                0.556,
                0.214
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(f_{+}^{\\prime}(0) = \\lim_{x\\to 0^{+}}\\frac{f(x) - f(0)}{x - 0} = \\lim_{x\\to 0^{+}}\\frac{1 - \\cos x}{x\\sqrt{x}} = 0;\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.139,
                0.222,
                0.528,
                0.254
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nf _ {-} ^ {\\prime} (0) = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {-}} \\frac {f (x) - f (0)}{x - 0} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {-}} x g (x) = 0,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.076,
                0.258,
                0.583,
                0.273
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\( f_{+}^{\\prime}(0) = f_{-}^{\\prime}(0) \\)，所以 \\( f(x) \\) 在 \\( x = 0 \\) 处可导，应选(D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.046,
                0.28,
                0.191,
                0.294
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.076,
                0.302,
                0.727,
                0.33
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】显然 \\(S(x)\\) 是以2为周期的偶函数，则 \\(S\\left(-\\frac{5}{2}\\right) = S\\left(-\\frac{1}{2}\\right) = S\\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\right)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.077,
                0.339,
                0.525,
                0.383
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "而 \\(S\\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\right) = \\frac{f\\left(\\frac{1}{2} - 0\\right) + f\\left(\\frac{1}{2} + 0\\right)}{2} = \\frac{3}{4}\\), 应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.046,
                0.39,
                0.191,
                0.404
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(4)【答案】 (B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.075,
                0.412,
                0.432,
                0.425
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 当 \\(m > n\\) 时，\\(r(\\mathbf{A}) \\leqslant n, r(\\mathbf{B}) \\leqslant n\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.076,
                0.432,
                0.499,
                0.446
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(r(\\mathbf{AB}) \\leqslant \\min \\{r(\\mathbf{A}), r(\\mathbf{B})\\}\\), 所以 \\(r(\\mathbf{AB}) \\leqslant n\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.076,
                0.453,
                0.571,
                0.467
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "于是 \\(r(\\mathbf{AB}) < m\\) ，即 \\(\\mathbf{AB}\\) 为降秩矩阵，故 \\(|\\mathbf{AB}| = 0\\) ，应选(B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.046,
                0.475,
                0.191,
                0.489
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（5）【答案】 (B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.075,
                0.496,
                0.552,
                0.51
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】因为 \\(X, Y\\) 相互独立且 \\(X \\sim N(0,1), Y \\sim N(1,1)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.076,
                0.519,
                0.552,
                0.545
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "所以 \\(X + Y\\sim N(1,2)\\) ，故 \\(P\\{X + Y\\leqslant 1\\} = \\frac{1}{2}\\) ，应选(B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.046,
                0.554,
                0.556,
                0.569
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "三、【解】 \\(z = xf(x + y)\\) 与 \\(F(x,y,z) = 0\\) 两边对 \\(\\mathcal{X}\\) 求导得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.248,
                0.576,
                0.743,
                0.643
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l l} { \\frac {\\mathrm {d} z}{\\mathrm {d} x} = f + x \\left(1 + \\frac {\\mathrm {d} y}{\\mathrm {d} x}\\right) f ^ {\\prime},} \\\\ { F _ {x} ^ {\\prime} + F _ {y} ^ {\\prime} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} y}{\\mathrm {d} x} + F _ {z} ^ {\\prime} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} z}{\\mathrm {d} x} = 0,} \\end{array} \\right. \\text {即} \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l l} {- x f ^ {\\prime} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} y}{\\mathrm {d} x} + \\frac {\\mathrm {d} z}{\\mathrm {d} x} = f + x f ^ {\\prime},} \\\\ { F _ {y} ^ {\\prime} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} y}{\\mathrm {d} x} + F _ {z} ^ {\\prime} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} z}{\\mathrm {d} x} = - F _ {x} ^ {\\prime},} \\end{array} \\right.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.073,
                0.648,
                0.531,
                0.682
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "解得 \\(\\frac{\\mathrm{d}z}{\\mathrm{d}x} = \\frac{(f + xf')F_y' - xf'F_x'}{F_y' + xf'F_z'}\\) （\\(F_{y}^{\\prime} + xf^{\\prime}F_{z}^{\\prime}\\neq 0)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.046,
                0.688,
                0.655,
                0.703
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "四、【解】令 \\(P(x,y) = \\mathrm{e}^{x}\\sin y - b(x + y)\\)，\\(Q(x,y) = \\mathrm{e}^{x}\\cos y - ax\\)，"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.327,
                0.71,
                0.666,
                0.738
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\frac {\\partial Q}{\\partial x} = \\mathrm {e} ^ {x} \\cos y - a, \\quad \\frac {\\partial P}{\\partial y} = \\mathrm {e} ^ {x} \\cos y - b,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.076,
                0.745,
                0.613,
                0.771
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nI = \\left(\\oint_ {L + \\overline {{O A}}} - \\int_ {\\overline {{O A}}}\\right) [ e ^ {x} \\sin y - b (x + y) ] d x + (e ^ {x} \\cos y - a x) d y,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.076,
                0.78,
                0.796,
                0.812
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "而 \\(\\oint_{L + \\overline{OA}}\\left[\\mathrm{e}^{x}\\sin y - b(x + y)\\right]\\mathrm{d}x + (\\mathrm{e}^{x}\\cos y - ax)\\mathrm{d}y = \\iint_{D}(b - a)\\mathrm{d}x\\mathrm{d}y = \\frac{\\pi}{2} (b - a)a^{2},\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.073,
                0.816,
                0.677,
                0.842
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\int_ {\\overline {{O A}}} \\left[ e ^ {x} \\sin y - b (x + y) \\right] d x + \\left(e ^ {x} \\cos y - a x\\right) d y = - \\int_ {0} ^ {2 a} b x d x = - 2 a ^ {2} b,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.073,
                0.852,
                0.509,
                0.877
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(I = \\frac{\\pi}{2} (b - a)a^2 + 2a^2 b = \\left(\\frac{\\pi}{2} + 2\\right)a^2 b - \\frac{\\pi}{2} a^3.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.046,
                0.885,
                0.599,
                0.901
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "五、【解】 方法一 曲线 \\(y = y(x)\\) 上任一点 \\(P(x,y)\\) 处的切线为"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.298,
                0.907,
                0.473,
                0.922
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nY - y = y ^ {\\prime} (X - x),\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "bbox": [
                0.716,
                0.815,
                0.924,
                0.917
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": null
        },
        {
            "type": "image_caption",
            "bbox": [
                0.793,
                0.919,
                0.851,
                0.931
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "五题图"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.101,
                0.074,
                0.757,
                0.102
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "令 \\(Y = 0\\) 得 \\(X = x - \\frac{y}{y'}\\)，切线与 \\(x\\) 轴的交点为 \\(Q\\left(x - \\frac{y}{y'}, 0\\right)\\)，垂足为 \\(T(x, 0)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.101,
                0.107,
                0.483,
                0.139
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(S_{1} = \\frac{1}{2}\\cdot \\frac{y}{y^{\\prime}}\\cdot y = \\frac{y^{2}}{2y^{\\prime}}, S_{2} = \\int_{0}^{x}y(t)\\mathrm{d}t,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.101,
                0.144,
                0.424,
                0.174
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(2S_{1} - S_{2} = 1\\) 得 \\(\\frac{y^2}{y'} -\\int_0^x y(t)\\mathrm{d}t = 1,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.101,
                0.18,
                0.388,
                0.197
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "两边对 \\(x\\) 求导并整理得 \\(yy^{\\prime \\prime} = y^{\\prime 2}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.101,
                0.204,
                0.488,
                0.233
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "令 \\(y^\\prime = p\\) ，则 \\(y^{\\prime \\prime} = p\\frac{\\mathrm{d}p}{\\mathrm{d}y}\\) 代入得 \\(y p\\frac{\\mathrm{d}p}{\\mathrm{d}y} = p^{2}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.101,
                0.238,
                0.602,
                0.27
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(p \\neq 0\\) ，所以 \\(\\frac{\\mathrm{d}p}{\\mathrm{d}y} - \\frac{1}{y} p = 0\\) ，解得 \\(p = C_1 \\mathrm{e}^{-\\int -\\frac{1}{y} \\mathrm{d}y} = C_1 y\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.101,
                0.277,
                0.518,
                0.305
